Request large file support. I could have used the T2 wrappers, but
decided to do it a bit more verbose.

  - Rene Rebe <rene@exactcode.de>

--- pdksh-5.2.14/Makefile.in.vanilla	2006-04-24 14:03:27.000000000 +0000
+++ pdksh-5.2.14/Makefile.in	2006-04-24 14:03:47.000000000 +0000
@@ -12,7 +12,7 @@
 INSTALL_PROGRAM = @INSTALL_PROGRAM@
 INSTALL_DATA = @INSTALL_DATA@
 
-DEFS = @DEFS@
+DEFS = @DEFS@ -D_FILE_OFFSET_BITS=64
 LIBS = @LIBS@
 
 CPPFLAGS = @CPPFLAGS@
